column5: Way to go man! 2 in one year HOLY CRAP!  Lew,  Man you are dialed in on that body of water LOL!  Hope they are still biting on Thanksgiving
In the old days 10% of fishermen caught 90% of the fish.  Now two guys seem to be catching all the big fish.  Nice job.  Those are beauts.
nice ski two 50'' awesome
Thanks for the replies everyone.  Terry - that picture is a classic.  I've got that one saved.  GCD-  Don't mind you asking at all.  Got her on a double cowgirl.
Wow 2 50's in the same season!! I would be buying loto tickets to go with that luck, congrats!!! Awesome photoshop Terry!!!  Cheers, 1leg
any time  if anyone else gets a 50+ muskie and wants it on my 50" bill just let me know and I will do it
A fish dreams are made off. Congrats and two yet.   RR
I'll take you up on that Terry!  SWEET fish MistyRiver1!!!
Very nice Jim!!!!  Maureen

Greetings everyone.  I just got back from our 12 days at Lakair with the family and friends.   It was an awesome time !!!!!!!!!!  I haven't got all my pictures loaded yet but did want to share this beauty.  Lew and I headed out last Monday morning and I landed this girl.   She measured 50 inches and had a 23 inch girth. Two 50 inch fish for me this year.....definitely have a horseshoe you know where.  Here she is...
WOW!!Nice.... luckylew we call him!
A great big beautiful fish, Jim. Congrats to you and Lew!
wow thats a beauty, at first i thought you ment 50" laker (lake trout)
what a tank!  nicely done
definitely a nice one...  thanks for sharing.
Beautiful fish for sure...fish of a lifetime...but 2 in the same year....unbelievable!!!  Jason
real nice fish
What a beautiful musky.  Congrats on your 2nd 50 of the season.  Well done.
Nice fish, Jiim.  Look forward to your report and additional pictures.  John
What a monster gorgeuos fish congrats to you..  Terry thats classic  Peps
What a beast! She's a beauty! Sounds like your having a great year!
Very nice, congrats.  I gotta get my face on one of den der 50 notes.
Attaboy Jim.  I was waiting to see this fish, been hearing a lot of rumors.   Well worth the wait.  Congrats.
Congratulations.  A real beauty and your second this year even!  Can I borrow that horseshoe?
A beautiful fish Jim, congrats!
You're on a roll Jim. Congrats!!
Nothing I can add to this because everything else has been said  WTG     Great looking ski!  Thanks for sharing Leechman
Very nice,them West Arm skiis are cooperating this year.Looks good on you! Joe
TJ, its only luck when you catch 'em  Lew has the skills  Nice fish there Jim, and the 2nd this year? Some of Lew must be rubbing off

Alright enough with the shenanigans...looks like that fish is trained. Lew must be like some kind of Musky Whisperer.  The fish hangs out in the same spot. Lew whistles and the thing jumps in the boat for a picture.  It's this kind of thing that gives fishermen a bad name....       ' ' ' ' ' ' ' LOL - Just Kidding  Great fish Misty glad your boyt got to see you guys in action. BTW can I borrow your horseshoe...
SWEET!!!  Good for you Jim, that's just awesome.  Makes the whole trip worthwhile eh  Joey
awesome fish! You are one lucky dude!
Great fish Jim, your going to have a tough time beating this summers action.  Mike
Beautiful fish Jim!!!  What did that one hit?... if you don't mind me askin'...
